# -*- Mode: Shell-Script -*-
# Getopt::Gen specification for 'dwdspp'
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
program "dwdspp"
#program_version "0.01"

purpose	"Tokenizer for the KDWDS project."
author  "Bryan Jurish <moocow@ling.uni-potsdam.de>"
on_reparse "warn"

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Details
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
details "
dwdspp is a pre-processor for raw text intended to be
used to prepare documents for PoS tagging by L<dwdst>.
"

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Arguments
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
argument "FILE(s)" "Input files" \
    details="See the L<--list> option."

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Options
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

int "verbose" v "Verbosity level." \
    arg="LEVEL" \
    default="1" \
    details="Range: 0..1"

string	"output" o "Write output to FILE." \
    arg="FILE" \
    default="-" \
    details="
Output files are in Brill format: one sentence per line, tokens
separated by whitespace.
"

flag "list" l "Arguments are input-file lists." \
    default="0" \
    details="
If this flag is given, the FILE(s) arguments should be lists
of input filenames, one filename per line, which should be
processed.  Otherwise, the FILE(s) arguments are interpreted
as filenames of the input files themselves.
"


#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Addenda
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Footer
#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
acknowledge "

This package was developed as part of the DWDS/Collocations project
('Kollokationen im digitalen W\"orterbuch der deutschen Sprache'
= 'collocations in the digital dictionary of the German language') at the
Berlin-Brandenburgische Akademie der Wissenschaften.
For details on the DWDS project, visit: http://www.dwds.de.

"

seealso "L<dwdst>."
